  <brief_title>Operative or Conservative Treatment of Acute Acromioclavicular Joint Dislocation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Operative or Conservative Treatment of Acute Acromioclavicular Joint Dislocation Rockwood Grade III and V - a Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
